    • Episode

      public Episode​(java.lang.String title, java.lang.String desc, java.net.URI link, PodcastPlayerModel.Podcast parent, int epNum)
      Initializes all of the metadata for the Episode. All of the below data is required, but any of it can be set to null if not applicable.
      Parameters:
      title - is the name of the Episode.
      desc - is a description of the Episode.
      link - is a link to the Episode.
      parent - is the Podcast in which this Episode is contained.
      epNum - is the number of the Episode in its parent Podcast.
